{"tid":1459763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"姨丈係深藍廢中，而家諗緊辦法聯同表妹送佢去大灣區","createTime":"2019-08-12T20:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T22:33:15.000Z","uid":58841,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a472a58d085c264049a0401bccc10d22fa4e1d71","tid":1459763,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:10:48.000Z","msg":"話說我老母深黃<br />\n日日係度屌柒政府黑警 話藍絲無良心快d仆街死<br />\n咁自然我老母個邊都係黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左個深藍姨丈<br />\n前日飲茶個陣又發生咁既事，我個日day off 打算飲完茶先去發夢<br />\n而表妹無理鳩佢一早發緊夢，所以唔係現場<br />\n深藍廢中：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表妹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班示威者收左錢係度搞事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾多錢呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3000呀聽講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係捉到告暴動坐十年八年喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢點會俾警察捉到呀，捉左都會放你走啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係有成幾百個而家俾人告喎，拿不如咁，表妹話俾十皮你企前線食催淚彈呀嘛，我而家加碼多十皮你去企前線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪搞我啦，d煙吸左都唔知有咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪就係囉，你寧願唔要廿皮都唔想去食煙，得個3000蚊我返幾日工已經有啦，洗撚區區為左少少錢去較飛呀<br />\n<br />\n個陣個氣氛已經俾佢搞到好沉重，我屋企人黑撚哂面唔想同佢嘈<br />\n<br />\n之後我wts俾表妹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你有個咁既深藍老豆真係慘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講左好多次啦，又勸唔聽，好想離家出走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇考慮過送佢返去共享大灣區榮耀 <a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/gds/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Fgds%2F&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB24aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=d911354a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/gds/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />🤔🤔👏🏻"},{"pid":"f346b92bbbc8d9e0c761f34cd411549801dffed6","tid":1459763,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:13:10.000Z","msg":"利申 表妹有經濟能力 離家出走可以住條仔屋企"},{"pid":"28cb7155c25961e85c878abb12fef0e2d04871fa","tid":1459763,"uid":305822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:13:23.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16962cf0bdabe806b4c0abdc769c066792943436","tid":1459763,"uid":35457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:32:48.000Z","msg":"呢個post好有趣，尤其最後個條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885a77ad039392eee3d670b806d08f9cd04b1490","tid":1459763,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:41:22.000Z","msg":"杜絕深藍廢老 由身邊人做起"},{"pid":"c44cad41b738bc6ad9faa36bcdb794a946764a5f","tid":1459763,"uid":174104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:49:17.000Z","msg":"辛苦你表妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，對牛彈琴"},{"pid":"e875781b3149206b7d291d3765a68abe0462f4fc","tid":1459763,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:59:09.000Z","msg":"啱喇送佢上福建啦"},{"pid":"9f2334249432999f1c5de2cbc112f68616aceae3","tid":1459763,"uid":105546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:00:51.000Z","msg":"恭喜你有個深黃嘅阿媽<br />\n祝佢長命百歲"},{"pid":"dd1cf5e0f53bada0d644e2e590578e25d1acea1d","tid":1459763,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f2334249432999f1c5de2cbc112f68616aceae3","tid":1459763,"uid":105546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:00:51.000Z","msg":"恭喜你有個深黃嘅阿媽<br />\n祝佢長命百歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:33:15.000Z","msg":"因為反送中單野同我老母破冰我算第一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}